{"tid":258760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京感謝習近平在高峰論壇的熱情接待","createTime":"2017-05-26T11:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T03:47:57.000Z","uid":118744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3cc2d4505de78dc972525e500553b122efd7803","tid":258760,"uid":118744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:21:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普京感謝習近平在一帶一路高峰論壇期間給予的熱情接待</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://sputniknews.cn/images/102271/67/1022716775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsputniknews.cn%2Fimages%2F102271%2F67%2F1022716775.jpg&h=20f6ea81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&copy; AFP 2017/ ALEXANDER ZEMLIANICHENKO<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯衛星通訊社莫斯科電 俄羅斯總統普京請中國外長王毅轉達對中國國家主席習近平的問候，同時感謝習近平主席在一帶一路高峰論壇期間給予的熱情接待。<br />\n<br />\n普京在會見中國外長王毅時說：&quot;俄中兩國全面戰略協作夥伴關係越來越密切。我們將您的此次到訪看作是籌備今年俄中關係大事件的重要階段，我指的是中國國家主席對俄羅斯進行正式訪問&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，26日王毅將與俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫進行工作會晤。<br />\n他說：&quot;我請您向中國國家主席、我的老朋友習近平先生轉達我最誠摯的問候，感謝他給予的熱情接待&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n普京表示，10天前俄羅斯代表團在中國參加大型國際活動期間得到了熱情接待。<br />\n<br />\n他說：&quot;我想再次對於活動取得的重大成功表示祝賀，這個活動的舉辦達到最高水平，而且恰逢其時，碩果累累&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n來源：俄羅斯衛星網<br />\n<a href=\"http://sptnkne.ws/e4tQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsptnkne.ws%2Fe4tQ&d=X4fZAkDwfXTc2TgTMdGF6L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3ad57999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sptnkne.ws/e4tQ</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<strong>相關新聞：</strong><br />\n<br />\n中國外長：中俄全面戰略協作夥伴關係不受任何外部因素影響<br />\n<a href=\"http://sptnkne.ws/e4tR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsptnkne.ws%2Fe4tR&d=X4fZAkDwfXTc2TgTMdGF6L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=704c0eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sptnkne.ws/e4tR</a>"},{"pid":"fe2439228ddf2ce21e2b9f0e7f25ece46dfd7099","tid":258760,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}